taines_dc_refmx_website_image_2x_wmko_standard-400x254.jpeg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/fontaines_dc_refmx_website_image_2x_wmko_standard-800x508.jpeg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/fontaines_dc_refmx_website_image_2x_wmko_standard-696x442.jpeg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/fontaines_dc_refmx_website_image_2x_wmko_standard-1392x884.jpeg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/fontaines_dc_refmx_website_image_2x_wmko_standard-1068x678.jpeg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/reading">雷丁和利兹</a>音乐节将于 2023 年回归，请查看下面两个音乐节举办地的最新天气预报。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/foals-reading-leeds-2023-line-up-interview-new-music-paramore-3363463">小马驹谈雷丁和利兹 2023：“这将成为完美的头条秀”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这两个音乐节将于 8 月 25 日至 27 日在 Richfield Avenue 和 Bramham Park 回归， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foals">Foals</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/imagine-dragons">Imagine Dragons</a>都将成为头条新闻。</p><p>最新的天气预报显示，雷丁和利兹在周末的大部分时间里都会有降雨和微风。在利兹，周六（8 月 26 日）参加节日的人们可能会遇到雷阵雨。</p><p>雷丁的最高气温将达到 23°，而利兹的气温将升至 20°。</p><p>您可以在下面查看雷丁和利兹的最新天气预报（来自<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/weather/rg1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC Weather</a> ）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3300774" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3300774" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3300774" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022.jpg" alt="读书节主舞台" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3300774" class="wp-caption-text">读书节主舞台。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>读书节</strong></h2><p><strong>8 月 24 日星期四：</strong>小雨和微风，最高气温 23°，最低气温 11°。</p><p> <strong>8 月 25 日星期五：</strong>小阵雨和微风，最高气温 19°，最低气温 10°。</p><p> <strong>8 月 26 日星期六：</strong>小雨和微风，最高气温 19°，最低气温 10°。</p><p> <strong>8 月 27 日星期日：</strong>云淡风轻，最高气温 19°，最低气温 10°。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cu6dLKgIrHq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 6